					<a class="button button--secondary" href="#workflow">See how it works</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero__visual" aria-hidden="true">
				<div class="hero__demo hero__demo--stack" data-hero-stack>
					<div class="hero__stack-card" data-hero-stack-card>
						<div class="hero__stack-inner">
							<div class="hero__stack-face hero__stack-face--notes">
								<div class="hero__notes-shell">
									<div class="hero__notes" data-hero-notes>
										<div class="hero__note" data-note>
											<span class="hero__note-time" data-note-time>09:05 AM</span>
											<p data-note-text>Rolled out auth refactor with @Payments. Routing tests green again.</p>
											<span class="hero__note-tags" data-note-tags>#shipping · @payments</span>
										</div>
										<div class="hero__note" data-note>
											<span class="hero__note-time" data-note-time>10:42 AM</span>
											<p data-note-text>Met with @Ops to unblock dashboards. Logged follow-up tasks for Friday.</p>
											<span class="hero__note-tags" data-note-tags>@ops · #analytics</span>
										</div>
										<div class="hero__note" data-note>
											<span class="hero__note-time" data-note-time>12:18 PM</span>
											<p data-note-text>Paired w/ @Sarah on bug bash. Closed 5 production issues.</p>
											<span class="hero__note-tags" data-note-tags>@sarah · #bugbash</span>
										</div>
										<div class="hero__note" data-note>
											<span class="hero__note-time" data-note-time>3:55 PM</span>
											<p data-note-text>Drafted blog on AI digests keeping execs synced. Need metrics tomorrow.</p>
											<span class="hero__note-tags" data-note-tags>@nico · #content</span>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="hero__funnel" data-hero-funnel>
									<span class="hero__funnel-glow"></span>
									<span class="hero__funnel-spinner"></span>
									<span class="hero__funnel-label" data-funnel-label>Synthesizing 4 notes…</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="hero__stack-face hero__stack-face--insight">
								<header>
									<span class="hero__insight-pill" data-insight-pill>Executive update</span>
									<span class="hero__insight-meta">AI output</span>
								</header>
								<h3 data-insight-title>Ready for meeting prep</h3>
								<p data-insight-body>
									Auth refactor shipped, payments are stable, and Ops dashboards are back online. Next focus: staging DB metrics for Friday.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<ul class="hero__metrics">
				<li>
					<strong>1 secure workspace</strong>
					<span>Entries, projects, people, analytics, and insights stay linked</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>7+ AI templates</strong>
					<span>Stand-up recap, X post, blog, review, exec update, ideas, custom</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Flexible delivery</strong>
					<span>On-demand outputs plus scheduled digests with timezone & lead time</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="section section--features" id="features">
			<div class="section__intro">
				<h2>Log once, repurpose everywhere</h2>
				<p>
					Purpose-built for technical teams who need trustworthy records, flexible AI outputs,
					and scheduled digests without extra busywork.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-grid">
				{features.map((feature) => (
					<article class="feature-card">
						<span class="feature-card__label">{feature.label}</span>
